ComicInfo.Summary:
THE RETURN OF JOHN SCHAEFER!
What is Dutch's brother doing on a Predator's game planet in the far reaches of space?! And more importantly - will he get in Theta's way?
The lifelong refugee has revenge to serve up - and she is not about to let it get cold.
Brisson and Manna's epic adventure continues!
